parameters: \n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Huh? Idiotic, such a thing...!?"
Ameria and Lyric collapsed to the ground, powerless.
\n<Lyric>"Haa... Ah-... I'm okay, I'm okay... Haa... Haa..."

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"You really surprise me... To think you'd give me so much
trouble..."

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Enough... Anything's fine... It's bothersome... Annoying...
At this rate, my head's going to burst..."
\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"That's exactly why! I've come to want you even more...!"

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Too bad for you! Even if you try to save Ameria, the
outcome won't change! You are destined to obey me!"

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"The miracle that grants wishes, Begi-Ade! And the
nourishment of lust to satiate the belly, the two of you!"

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Ah, I want, I want, I want...! I want you! Give me
everything of you!"

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Come here! Take my hand! But never give up until the very
end! Resistance is the finest spice that colors desire! It
becomes the supreme nectar!"

\n<Lyric>"Hehe... Ahh~... I'm exhausted. I'm really a bit tired
now..."

\n<Ameria>"Uh... I'm sorry... It's my fault that things turned out
like this..."
\n<Lyric>"Alright... Let's do this... Leave the back to me...!"

\n<Roselitte>"...You two should step back. You must be at your limit
after that battle, right?"

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Nfufufufu... You alone? That's rich! After all, you
couldn't do anything by yourself until now!"
\n<Roselitte>"Indeed, I couldn't do anything on my own..."

\n<Roselitte>"I even died twice, and each time, miracles were performed
to save me..."
\n<Roselitte>"But that's not all... All this time, always..."

\n<Roselitte>"Always, Ameria and Lyric have...! They've been helping
me...!"
\n<Roselitte>"They fought with their lives on the line for us...!"
\n<Roselitte>"I have! Many people have been saved by them!"
$gameScreen.spine(33).setSkeleton('ローゼリッテ_ラストバトル')
\n<Roselitte>"How can I, a knight, fail to protect them!!"

\n<Lyric>"If you exert all your strength like that, your body won't
be able to take it! You might not be saved again, you
know!?"

\n<Roselitte>"Lyric... it's enough. If I can fight for you, I don't care
what happens to my body."
\n<Ameria>"Wait, stop! Please don't do anything rash!"

\n<Ameria>"I don't want to see Roselitte suffering anymore! I'll do my
best too! So... so please...!"

\n<Roselitte>"Ameria... I'm sorry. Right now, I live for your sake. So
please... let me be unreasonable this last time."

\n<Roselitte>"It was fun. Though it was a short time, I never thought
traveling with friends could be this enjoyable."

\n<Roselitte>"This life that was saved by the two of you, I want to use
it for you..."
\n<Roselitte>"I will carve out a future for the two of you...!!"
\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Ahahahahaha! Is that your true nature, Roselitte!"

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"But recklessness isn't good, you know!? --Monsters, trample
Roselitte!"

\n<Roselitte>"I am one of the twelve knights of the Valam Empire's
Imperial Guard! Roselitte Schwarz!"

\n<Roselitte>"For the crime of ravaging the land of Valam, atone with
your body! Know that my sword is the judgment of Valam!
And--!"
\n<Roselitte>"Receive the retribution for hurting my friends!!"

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Truly... unexpected, this is... such a thing... I can't
understand it..."

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Hehe... even if you cut me down... it's not over... you
will surely come to regret this...!"

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"But... it's too late...! You will surely regret not coming
to me...!"
\n<Ameria>"Roselitte! We did it! It's all over now!"
\n<Ameria>"Why... The healing spell isn't working... Once more!"
\n<Lyric>"...Don't get your hopes up too much."

\n<Roselitte>"...I just want you to stay by my side for a little
while..."
\n<Ameria>"--No, no! Roselitte-san! I don't want you to die!!"

\n<Ameria>"I promised to heal you, Roselitte-san...! I'm sorry... I'm
so sorry...!! I'm sorry, Roselitte-san...!!"
\n<Roselitte>"Ameria... The one who should be apologizing... is me..."
\n<Roselitte>"Thank you for protecting me... I'm glad... I met you..."
\n<Lyric>"...You must be tired. Take a rest."
\n<Lyric>"It's okay. I'll take care of everything."
